      {
        "type": "appStoreReviewDetails",
        "id": "fff07c89-ed65-4c52-92bb-2f5d361246f7",
        "attributes": {
          "contactFirstName": "Sankalp",
          "contactLastName": "Thakur",
          "contactPhone": "+919111035899",
          "contactEmail": "shaurya@climitra.com",
          "demoAccountName": null,
          "demoAccountPassword": null,
          "demoAccountRequired": false,
          "notes": "Thank you for reviewing Astronova.\n\nDEMO ACCOUNT\nNot required. Astronova supports two entry paths:\n- Sign in with Apple (recommended for persistence)\n- \"Continue without signing in\" guest flow on the welcome screen\nEither path reaches every feature.\n\nWALKTHROUGH (3 MINUTES)\n1. Launch -> entertainment disclaimer -> Onboarding.\n2. Tap \"Continue without signing in\" at the bottom of the welcome card.\n3. Enter sample birth profile:\n   - Name: Astro Reviewer\n   - DOB: 14 March 1990\n   - Time: 09:15 AM (toggle \"Unknown\" off for full chart math)\n   - Place: type \"New Delhi\" and pick the suggestion\n4. Generate Chart -> Self tab renders the birth chart. Switch North-Indian / South-Indian layouts at the top.\n5. Time Travel tab -> Dasha Chakra wheel shows current mahadasha/antardasha. Drag to scrub years.\n6. Discover tab -> Today's Cosmic Weather across 7 domains; tap any card to expand.\n7. Temple tab -> astrologer listings + pooja offerings. Tapping Book surfaces the paywall (dismissible).\n8. Oracle / Chat tab -> first 3 questions are free; paywall after that (dismissible).\n9. Settings: privacy toggles, sign out, delete account, export data.\n\nBACKEND\nProduction backend is https://astronova-ghcr.onrender.com (Render). Health check returns 200.\nPrevious host astronova.onrender.com is being retired; please reference the GHCR host.\n\nIN-APP PURCHASES / SUBSCRIPTIONS\n- astronova_pro_monthly (auto-renewable, ready)\n- Astronova_pro_12_month_commitment (auto-renewable, may show MISSING_METADATA in ASC; the app falls back to monthly automatically if the annual product is unavailable. No code change required.)\n- Consumable IAPs: astronova_relationship_report, astronova_career_report, astronova_2026_yearly_report\n- Chat-credit IAPs: astronova_chat_credits_5 / _20 / _50\n\nPERMISSIONS\n- Camera + Microphone: only requested when joining a video session with an astrologer.\n- Contacts: only requested when picking a friend in compatibility flow. Contact identity is not transmitted.\n- No location services (place-of-birth is server-side geocoded from user-entered text).\n- Notifications are opt-in inside Settings.\n\nCONTENT POSTURE\n- No user-generated content visible to other users.\n- No social/strangers messaging. Oracle is bot-only (user <-> app).\n- No gambling, contests, or advertising.\n- No medical/legal/financial claims. Disclaimers shown at launch and in Self footer.\n\nTHIRD-PARTY SERVICES\n- Render (backend host)\n- Swiss Ephemeris (server-side astronomy)\n- OpenAI (Oracle; deterministic fallback if unavailable, so review never blocks)\n- Sign in with Apple (auth)\n- Smartlook Analytics package referenced but NOT linked in this build.\n\nKNOWN EDGE CASES\n1. \"Unknown\" birth time accepted; reading marked approximate, Lagna falls back to dawn-time.\n2. Annual subscription may show MISSING_METADATA - app handles gracefully (see above).\n3. Render free-tier cold-start of 5-10 seconds on first request after idle; the Discover tab shows a skeleton loader.\n\nCONTACT\nSankalp Thakur, +91 91110 35899, shaurya@climitra.com\nResponse within 24 hours during review."
        },
